data.title: Andrei Kirilenko news and rumors - Page 2
data.text:
News

Andrei Kirilenko out of Hollins' rotation

It appears Andrei Kirilenko is on the outside of coach Lionel Hollins’ rotation when the Nets have everyone healthy.

Injuries

Nets’ Kirilenko out with back issues

Andrei Kirilenko, after missing 25 of the first 29 games last season with back spasms, sat out Sunday morning’s practice because of a tight lower back.

Incidents

Andrei Kirilenko’s Utah home burglarized

Andrei Kirilenko's Salt Lake home was burglarized over the weekend, something that surprised his wife who calls the city the "safest place on Earth."

Statements

Nets' Andrei Kirilenko rips Jason Kidd

In a wide-ranging interview with SovSport, the Russian sports tabloid, Andrei Kirilenko offers some telling criticism of Jason Kidd.

NBA market

Kirilenko returning to Nets for 2nd year of deal

Andrei Kirilenko will return to the Nets after opting into the final year of his contract, according to his agent.

Injuries

Nets' Garnett, Kirilenko could return within week

The Brooklyn Nets say Kevin Garnett is hoping to return from a back injury next weekend or during their trip to Florida on April 8-9.
